The video material was digitally redone and many color filters were applied. The movie went from having a Blueish/Greenish 'Tint' to an Orange/Red tone (apparently because that would make it a stylistic match with the 2004 sequel 'Innocence'). [2.0] Features new audio and updated 3D graphics, some of the dialogue was changed and some minor scenes were cut.
